{"tid":766322,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線！啱啱捉到公司個新仔偷偷去咗食宵夜！","createTime":"2018-08-03T13:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T15:31:35.000Z","uid":34934,"like":4,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"22bce8fd89bdefaa03ccdfa3d876ddbd6f6ae984","tid":766322,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"痴撚線！<br />\n話說岩岩叫條新仔落去見個細客！<br />\n我見佢急急腳出左去覺得有唔陀 <br />\n咪跟住佢尾順手買包小食囉<br />\n<br />\n點知比我見到佢入左間大家樂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果一刻真係好失望  公司用心盆栽倍佢<br />\n日日比好多野佢做 比佢學多 d 野<br />\n估唔到佢咁仆街用公司時間食宵夜  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我襯佢買完飛拎完餐坐埋位果時即刻衝入去捉佢<br />\n我當場屌爆佢問佢係咪痴撚左線   fuck<br />\n跟住佢就乖乖地跟我走左 <br />\n個豬排飯 油菜 凍奶茶 完全無食過  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗果到都成 $40  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985a3700e2c8d7903a357210bd76c0d0074aa97c","tid":766322,"uid":31024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"402913ac4f4f54187ba69c2a8295f86098ae3bb5","tid":766322,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"樓主醒目到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5511566b0b9c180592aef93dfea516fc9772eac1","tid":766322,"uid":58811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"6b662f84f8a52038a20b24ff0af7550854af54b1","tid":766322,"uid":87506,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢叫用心盆栽倍佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a114c6c50fd5b185b90226ca2c5cc808e74e3a","tid":766322,"uid":192234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"重作啦<img src=\"/as